A cyberpunk-style digital interface floating in a neon-lit void, displaying an intricate holographic address book system with cascading layers of glowing contact cards, filter panels, and organizational hierarchies branching like neural networks. Each contact card pulses with bio-metric data visualizations, connection strength indicators, and geographic heat signatures. The interface features sleek translucent panels in electric blue and hot pink, with data streams flowing between interconnected nodes representing relationships and communication patterns. Floating tags and category badges orbit around the central search matrix like satellites. The scene is viewed from a slight angle, emphasizing depth and the overwhelming complexity of modern contact management, bathed in atmospheric fog and volumetric light rays cutting through the digital darkness.
